{"tid":2099472,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"德國電訊否認加強與華為合作","createTime":"2020-07-08T08:58:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-09T08:29:52.000Z","uid":47492,"like":17,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"f5668f8f645483ca633e3636b221839833c64678","tid":2099472,"uid":47492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T08:58:44.000Z","msg":"德國電訊(Deutsche Telekom)否認其不顧安全當局的警告，加強與中國電訊設備商華為商業關係的報道。<br />\n<br />\n德國《商報》(Handelsblatt)引述內部文件指出，德國電訊在5G網絡、雲端服務等業務上均依賴華為作為供應商；還要求華為在德國向其提供優於競爭對手的技術優勢，以確保在5G網絡的領先地位。兩家公司並同意在德國電訊的5G網絡上，更多地使用「不含美國製品」的組件。<br />\n德國電訊發言人回應稱，有關報道有違事實，公司在過去三年已縮減與華為的生意往來。德國電訊亦多次重申，其將在核心移動網絡等安全關鍵領域，完全擺脫與中國供應商的合作。"},{"pid":"8694b4f412f5071aa018f82422399e64b6d059c6","tid":2099472,"uid":47492,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T08:59:01.000Z","msg":"[url]<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/international/article/2516965/url]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Finternational%2Farticle%2F2516965%2Furl%5D&d=68p4wiGQQ1h%2Fwz3iobjDKyvt59O44HeJS3%2BtxtDyp5g%3D&h=55d9159a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/international/article/2516965/url]</a>"},{"pid":"e8e3dad39f76e168eb4ccc4e37ac369dc37d5908","tid":2099472,"uid":343361,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T09:01:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁夠薑落肥婆面<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我鍾意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"84b58b5da40ab32993e1c5e80e9d3c023e589ed4","tid":2099472,"uid":345502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e8e3dad39f76e168eb4ccc4e37ac369dc37d5908","tid":2099472,"uid":343361,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T09:01:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁夠薑落肥婆面<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我鍾意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal